entries.femaleVariant: Fuck you lookin' at? Nothin' to see here – move along!
What's going on?
Stop it or else you'll kill him.
What's goin' on here?
Take it easy, or you'll kill 'im.
Is this how you protect and serve?
This your first day in Night City? What's it fuckin' look like?
Get outta here, piss-ant!
Yeah, and? He your brother or somethin'? The fuck you care?
Oh, is this how Night City's finest "protect and serve"?
entries.maleVariant: Is this how Night City's finest "protect and serve"?

entries.femaleVariant: Don't care – don't know 'im.
So, why the fuck we talkin'?
He put a girl into a coma. Daughter of a friend.
Like to know what's goin' on around me. Not every day you see a man in a thousand-eddie suit gettin' beaten within an inch of his life. Wouldn't you agree?
entries.maleVariant: I like to know what's goin' on around me. It's not every day you see a man in a thousand-eddie suit gettin' beaten within an inch of his life. Wouldn't you agree?

entries.femaleVariant: Leave him alone.
I'll deal with him.
I was just about to leave.
I was just leaving, officer. Enjoy your evening.
Leave him alone.
From what I can tell, your guy's a mid-level manager.
See this badge? That means I can do whatever the fuck I want!
And?
Corp won't let this slide. They'll pull the data from this asshole's biomon and find you. And then, they'll shoot you.
entries.maleVariant: The corp won't let this slide. They'll pull the data from this asshole's biomon and find you. And then, they'll shoot you.

entries.femaleVariant: Rise and shine, corpo-swine...
[Wake]
Akh... oh fuck... khe khe...
Heard you've been showing spiked braindances.
The truth. What did they want from you?
Eddies.
Heard you've been showin' girls XBDs. You know – kind where your nose bleeds, your mouth froths, brain fries a little...
No, no, no, no... Wait, I didn't know... Pusher must've sold me a bad batch...
Bullshit. Corpo-scum like you don't get their merch on random street corners. You know what you're watchin', and what you're showin' to others.
All right, all right, it's like... You know how it is when... when you want to get a girl in a club, right?
The truth. What did they want from you?
entries.maleVariant: The truth. What do they want from you?

entries.femaleVariant: I-I-I have no idea. They said somethin' about some slut a-and a virtu...
Is it really that hard to figure out? I'll give you a hint. It starts with "euro" and ends with "dollars."
Yeah... yeah, no, of course... you need a reward... I-is this enough?
Go on, get outta here.
Hand over your eddies.
[Punch]
[Shoot]
Nothing. It's your lucky day.
Nice chattin' with ya. Now hand over the eddies.
You know what I want? For suit 'n' tie slimebags like you to disappear from Night City. For the NCPD to lock you up for good.
I could've killed you. As a matter of fact, I still want to pretty badly.
Take this, you corpo bastard!
Keep walkin', before you end up like him.
Why? You wanna be some kinda hero?
Rotten skiff or an XBD?
Second one.
Mhm, yeah.
You think I don't know that? Fuckin' corpos walkin' around like holy cows in a two piece. But I ain't lettin' 'im go. No fuckin' chance.
Yeah? And what's in it for you?
Nothin'. It's just how I unwind.
All right, let's go, boys.
Take care of yourself... Officer.
Shit... khe khe... If it wasn't for you, I'd be... well, thank you. Were you sent by the company?
Wrong answer.
Then... hold on... Whaddaya want from me?
Nothin'.
I... I don't... I don't believe you. You saved me just like that, because you... felt like it?
Don't measure others by your own yardstick. Prick.
You know it's not if you're askin'. Don't make me finish what the badges started.
OK... Here! Here, here... Tha-that's everything I have on me...
Have a pleasant evening.
But you just need a little... a-a nudge in the right direction.
But when I asked what I had to do with it, they started beating on me so hard I thought I'd die.
Ah, this city's really going down the drain. For the police to do this, in plain sight, for no reason...
Go on, get outta here.
But... I don't understand... Just like that? For nothing in return?
But that wouldn't change a damn thing. Waste of lead, in fact. City's teemin' with others just waitin' to replace you.
entries.maleVariant: But that wouldn't change a damn thing. A waste of lead, in fact. City's teemin' with others just waitin' to replace you.

entries.femaleVariant: Now get the fuck outta my sight. Make me sick just lookin' at you.
entries.maleVariant: Now get the fuck outta my sight. You make me sick just lookin' at ya.

entries.femaleVariant: Agh! Gah, what the hell was that for?
If I see you again, or hear that you're jackin' girls into virtus, infected or otherwise...
To be honest with you... I have no idea. But I'm guessin' you do.
entries.maleVariant: To be honest with ya... I have no idea. But I'm guessin' you do.

entries.femaleVariant: Somethin' in this whole story of yours just... doesn't sit right with me.
entries.maleVariant: Somethin' in this whole story of yours... it just doesn't sit right with me.

entries.femaleVariant: I'm not really in the mood for an interrogation, but if I was... I've got a feeling you'd have more than a black eye to worry about.
I'll put you in a coma you'll never wake up from. Do you understand?
I... I-I understand!
Now get the fuck outta my sight. Make me sick...
entries.maleVariant: Now get the fuck outta my sight. You make me sick...

entries.femaleVariant: Agh! Psychos... city of fucking psychos!
Get outta my sight. Chop-chop, on the double.
That'll do.
Give me everything you've got.
That'll do. Now run off to your little castle made of glass before you run into someone who won't be so understanding.
entries.maleVariant: That'll do. Now, run off to your little castle made of glass before you run into someone who won't be so understanding.

entries.femaleVariant: Thank you! You have my gratitude.
Cocksuckin' suits.
I'm not asking you to. What I want is for you to let me finish the job.
Time to wake up.
